{
  "id": "L3F",
  "title": "At the Supermarket",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Welcome to the supermarket! In this lesson, you'll learn how to ask for help and find what you need. Let's start by getting an employee's attention."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Excusez-moi",
        "meaning": "Excuse me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Où est... ?",
        "meaning": "Where is... ?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In French, nouns have a gender. 'Le' is used for masculine nouns, like 'le pain' (the bread)."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V01",
      "data": {
        "le lait": "the milk"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V02",
      "data": {
        "le pain": "the bread"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Et... ?",
        "meaning": "And... ?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L3F_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "lait",
        "phonetic": "[lɛ]",
        "tip": "The 'ai' sounds like the 'e' in 'bet'. The final 't' is silent."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3F_S01",
      "title": "Asking for Help",
      "setting": "You're in a supermarket and need to find milk and bread. You see an employee stocking shelves.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Get the employee's attention",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask where the milk is",
          "chatbot_message": "Bonjour. Oui ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask where the bread is",
          "chatbot_message": "Le lait est là-bas."
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge their help",
          "chatbot_message": "Le pain est à côté."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great! Now let's learn how to ask for specific quantities and see if something is on sale."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je voudrais...",
        "meaning": "I would like..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "s'il vous plaît",
        "meaning": "please"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V03",
      "data": {
        "cinq cents grammes de": "five hundred grams of"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V04",
      "data": {
        "les raisins": "the grapes"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V05",
      "data": {
        "le fromage": "the cheese"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "...est en promotion ?",
        "meaning": "...is on sale?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Merci",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L3F_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "fromage",
        "phonetic": "[fʁɔmaʒ]",
        "tip": "The 'age' ending sounds like 'ahj', similar to the 'age' in 'massage'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3F_S02",
      "title": "Buying Fruit",
      "setting": "The employee is still with you. You want to buy some grapes and ask about cheese.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask for 500 grams of grapes",
          "chatbot_message": "Autre chose ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask if the cheese is on sale",
          "chatbot_message": "Voilà. Et avec ça ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the employee",
          "chatbot_message": "Oui, le fromage est en promotion."
        },
        {
          "title": "Respond to the employee",
          "chatbot_message": "De rien."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Excellent work! You have your items. Now it's time to go to the checkout. Let's learn the final phrases you'll need."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonjour",
        "meaning": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je peux avoir... ?",
        "meaning": "Can I have... ?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3F_V06",
      "data": {
        "un sac": "a bag"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ça fait... euros",
        "meaning": "That's... euros"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Par carte",
        "meaning": "By card"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Au revoir",
        "meaning": "Goodbye"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3F_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonne journée",
        "meaning": "Have a good day"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3F_S03",
      "title": "At the Checkout",
      "setting": "You are at the checkout ('la caisse'). The cashier greets you.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Greet the cashier",
          "chatbot_message": "Bonjour."
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for a bag",
          "chatbot_message": "Ce sera tout ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Respond to the total and pay",
          "chatbot_message": "Bien sûr. Ça fait 15 euros."
        },
        {
          "title": "Say goodbye",
          "chatbot_message": "Merci. Au revoir et bonne journée !"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}